summary: Exploring just the right balance between understanding brand behaviour and powerful execution, Safi Graauw is a self-taught director with an academic background in earth-sciences. Interweaving a strong narrative and sense of aesthetic in his imagery, his commercial work combines diversity and popular culture with a sense of entertainment.
